revised instructions;

1; unrar.

2; copy the orb file that you want to use to the same folder as the w7 button changer.

3; right click w7 buton changer run as admin.

4; click change, select the orb file you have just copied, thats it.

If you dont copy the orb file to the w7 button changer folder then your system will crash.
